msgid ""
"• Multi-instance browser support\n"
"• Per-app rotating vinyl record album art\n"
"• Animated tonearm\n"
"• Smooth animations\n"
"• Double-click to toggle vinyl per app\n"
"• Triple-click album art to show synced lyrics\n"
"• Single-click lyrics panel to return to album art\n"
